<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٠٩٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6700">أَبُو الْوَلِيدِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6018">مُخَارِقٍ </a>سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2971">طَارِقًا </a>قَالَ: قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">عَبْدُ اللهِ </a>: <span class="c2">«إِنَّ أَحْسَنَ الْحَدِيثِ كِتَابُ اللهِ، وَأَحْسَنَ الْهَدْيِ هَدْيُ مُحَمَّدٍ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>